  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Manipur</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Manipur experiences monsoon (May-September), pleasant autumn (October-November), cool winter (December-February) and warm spring (March-April). October to March offers ideal weather with clear skies, comfortable temperatures and excellent visibility for exploring natural sites and attending festivals.</p>
